&lt;p&gt;As a Data Science Team Leader, you will lead a talented team of data scientists while maintaining hands-on involvement in complex technical projects. You will be responsible for recruiting, mentoring, and developing team members while ensuring the delivery of high-impact machine learning solutions for fraud detection and risk assessment.&lt;/p&gt;
