&lt;li&gt;Be the primary point of contact for our most important merchants. Build, monitor, and communicate our KPIs to our clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct in-depth analysis of our customers&#39; most productive ways to utilize Riskified’s solution, including identifying and leading upsell opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide strategic analysis and critical thinking as we plan long-term expansion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with all other teams within the company to optimize customer experience across our portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist new customers as they join Riskified’s platform and begin using our services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
