&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our FP&amp;amp;A team is growing and we’re looking for a highly motivated and proactive FP&amp;amp;A Analyst to join us. The role will focus on driving corporate budgeting, forecasting processes, and financial analysis to support company growth. You will bring strong analytical abilities to collaborate closely with stakeholders, delivering the data driven insights needed to guide key business decisions and drive strategic initiatives forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
