&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Fraud Data Analyst to work directly with our customers on our Merchant Health Team. You will be part of a growing analytics team that is responsible for Riskified’s customers’ performance and online fraud prevention using quick problem-solving skills in real time. You will own a major part in researching and investigating new online-fraud trends and stand at the forefront of Riskified’s work. You’ll leverage your data analysis skills and knowledge of our product to provide meaningful insights directly to our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
