&lt;p&gt;This role combines product leadership, commercial ownership, and ecosystem strategy. You will operate as a domain GM, defining the strategy, tailoring the product experience, aligning cross-functional execution, and ensuring we build a scalable and profitable solution.&lt;/p&gt;
