&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Partner Marketing Manager to support and scale our global partner marketing efforts, with a strong focus on strategic events like our hosted flagship event Ascend and key co-marketing initiatives. This role is a critical part of our Demand Generation engine, helping us extend our reach through partners and create high-value, high-touch experiences for our target accounts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on, execution-focused role. You’ll be working closely with Field Marketing, Partnerships, Sales, and Content to bring partner programs to life across regions. From Ascend to partner-led campaigns and events, you’ll help ensure we are showing up in a strategic, consistent, and impactful way alongside our partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is designed to strengthen how we leverage partners across the business, while upleveling the partner experience within our most important programs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own execution of partner marketing programs across global initiatives including Ascend, NRF, MRC, Shoptalk, and co-marketing campaigns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development and execution of the partner strategy for Ascend, including sponsors, activations, and onsite experience (Partner Summit)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Field Marketing to align partner involvement with regional GTM plans and event strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help bring partner-led experiences to life across executive events, sidecars, and regional programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute joint campaigns with key partners including webinars, content, and ABX plays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Sales, BD, and Partnerships to identify the right partners for target accounts and key moments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure partner messaging and positioning aligns with our overall brand and campaign strategy- update portals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage partner deliverables and timelines to ensure seamless execution across programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to uplevel partner engagement into more white-glove, high-impact experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support reporting and tracking of partner program performance and contribution to pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track, analyze, and report on performance, translating data into clear insights and optimizations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Marketing Ops to ensure proper tracking, attribution, and campaign visibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
