&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 to 4 years of experience in marketing or partner marketing, ideally in B2B SaaS or tech&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge and curiosity to explore AI tools in order to create efficiencies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical mindset and comfort working with data to drive decisions and optimizations&lt;/li&gt;
