&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a talented multi disciplinary &lt;strong&gt;Senior Data Platform Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;with passion for infrastructure, who will be responsible for the performance, scale, and stability of our core data platform products. We are a data-driven organization, ingesting data at high rates, with demands increasing each day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Data Platform Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;, you will be part of the Data Platform group and will be responsible for a large scale production data platform that serves as the core infrastructure of our products. You&#39;ll develop self-service tools that support the accessibility of our platform for the use of our users from R&amp;amp;D and Analytics departments. We will look to you to be a center of knowledge, consult, and share your expertise with others.&lt;/p&gt;
