&lt;li&gt;Administrate, provision and monitor our different platform products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, maintain and enhance the Applicational infrastructure that is working tightly with our Data Platform infrastructure tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide development teams and mentor other team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use your creativity to resolve complex and high scale data related issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research new technologies, starting from POC level to production grade systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
