&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of distributed systems, in terms of ingestion, storage and access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with Data Streaming technologies: Apache Kafka / Apache Pulsar / Spark Streaming / Kstream / Apache Flink&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B.Sc. in Computer Science (or equivalent)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working on high scale, production-grade projects&lt;/li&gt;
