&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Full-Stack Developer in Riskified’s Core Services Group, you’ll build and maintain applications end-to-end using various technologies. Working in a dynamic, agile environment with cutting-edge technologies, you’ll contribute to expanding Riskified’s ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our developers take full ownership, from feature planning with Product and Design to selecting technologies, designing architecture, coding, reviewing, deploying in a CI/CD environment, and monitoring post-deployment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team focuses on customer-facing applications, including a core web tool that allows merchants to review orders, perform actions, and gain insights through advanced analytics. Whether you’re crafting precise UI, developing robust backend logic, or optimizing infrastructure for scale, you’ll have the opportunity to engage end-to-end.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Stack: Scala, Spark, Node.js, Ruby, React, Postgres, Elastic, Redis, AWS, Kafka, Docker, Kubernetes, CircleCI and much more.&lt;/p&gt;
