&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data-Driven Insights:&lt;/strong&gt; Use people analytics to identify trends, provide recommendations, and measure the success of HR initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Work closely with the global HR team to align local NY initiatives with our global people strategy and values.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
